o-roi-bang-word.html\/#Huong_dan_thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Word_chuyen_nghiep\" title=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Word chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Word chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-bang-word.html\/#Buoc_1_File_-%3E_New_-%3E_Nhap_tu_khoa_vao_o_Search_online_templates\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:\u00a0File\u00a0&#8211;&gt;\u00a0New\u00a0&#8211;&gt; Nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u00e0o \u00f4\u00a0Search online templates\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:\u00a0File\u00a0&#8211;>\u00a0New\u00a0&#8211;> Nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u00e0o \u00f4\u00a0Search online templates<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-bang-word.html\/#Buoc_2_Ban_nhap_tu_khoa_Brochures_va_nhap_vao_tim_kiem\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: B\u1ea1n nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a\u00a0Brochures v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm.\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: B\u1ea1n nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a\u00a0Brochures v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm.<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-bang-word.html\/#Buoc_3_Chon_Create\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ch\u1ecdn Create\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ch\u1ecdn Create<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-bang-word.html\/#Buoc_4_Sau_khi_chinh_sua_xong_ban_co_the_chon_in_CtrlP_de_in_ra_hoac_Ctrl_S_de_luu_lai\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Sau khi ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda xong, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn in\u00a0Ctrl+P\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 in ra ho\u1eb7c\u00a0Ctrl+ S\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Sau khi ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda xong, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn in\u00a0Ctrl+P\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 in ra ho\u1eb7c\u00a0Ctrl+ S\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00f4ng ty c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <\/em><em>Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0: Photoshop. <\/em><em style=\"font-size: inherit;\">B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 thu\u00ea ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cho m\u00ecnh. <\/em><em>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1n c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n<strong> thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Word<\/strong> th\u1eadt chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1o t\u1edd r\u01a1i ngay trong Word gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c t\u1edd r\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u1edf b\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch\u00a0<span id=\"cph1_lblRes\">T\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch (Booklet) tr\u00ean Word th\u00ec \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o trong Word<\/span>.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng powerpoint<\/a><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2961\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2961\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2961\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/b\u1ed9-office-c\u1ee7a-microsoft-cho-ph\u00e9p-b\u1ea1n-nhi\u1ec1u-t\u00ednh-n\u0103ng.jpg\" alt=\"thiet ke to roi\" width=\"825\" height=\"423\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/b\u1ed9-office-c\u1ee7a-microsoft-cho-ph\u00e9p-b\u1ea1n-nhi\u1ec1u-t\u00ednh-n\u0103ng.jpg 824w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/b\u1ed9-office-c\u1ee7a-microsoft-cho-ph\u00e9p-b\u1ea1n-nhi\u1ec1u-t\u00ednh-n\u0103ng-300x154.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/b\u1ed9-office-c\u1ee7a-microsoft-cho-ph\u00e9p-b\u1ea1n-nhi\u1ec1u-t\u00ednh-n\u0103ng-768x393.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2961\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ed9 office c\u1ee7a Microsoft cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Word_chuyen_nghiep\"><\/span><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Word chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1<\/strong>:\u00a0<strong>File\u00a0<\/strong>--><strong>\u00a0New\u00a0<\/strong>--> Nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u00e0o \u00f4\u00a0<strong>Search online templates<\/strong><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2962\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2962\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2962\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eadp-t\u1eeb-kh\u00f3a-flyerposter-\u0111\u1ec3-t\u00ecm-m\u1eabu.png\" alt=\"h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf poster qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" width=\"825\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eadp-t\u1eeb-kh\u00f3a-flyerposter-\u0111\u1ec3-t\u00ecm-m\u1eabu.png 1279w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eadp-t\u1eeb-kh\u00f3a-flyerposter-\u0111\u1ec3-t\u00ecm-m\u1eabu-300x179.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eadp-t\u1eeb-kh\u00f3a-flyerposter-\u0111\u1ec3-t\u00ecm-m\u1eabu-768x458.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eadp-t\u1eeb-kh\u00f3a-flyerposter-\u0111\u1ec3-t\u00ecm-m\u1eabu-1024x610.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2962\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a flyer,poster \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1eabu<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_2_Ban_nhap_tu_khoa_Brochures_va_nhap_vao_tim_kiem\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2<\/strong>: B\u1ea1n nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a\u00a0<strong>Brochures<\/strong> v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 cho b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2963\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2963\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2963\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-m\u1eabu-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-b\u1ea1n-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-tham-kh\u1ea3o.png\" alt=\"m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf\" width=\"825\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-m\u1eabu-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-b\u1ea1n-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-tham-kh\u1ea3o.png 1144w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-m\u1eabu-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-b\u1ea1n-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-tham-kh\u1ea3o-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-